name hyphen-ethiopic
category TLCore
revision 78069
shortdesc Hyphenation patterns for Ethiopic scripts.
longdesc Hyphenation patterns for languages written using the Ethiopic
longdesc script for Unicode engines. They are not supposed to be
longdesc linguistically relevant in all cases and should, for proper
longdesc typography, be replaced by files tailored to individual
longdesc languages.
depend hyph-utf8
depend hyphen-base
execute AddHyphen 	name=ethiopic synonyms=amharic,geez 	lefthyphenmin=1 	righthyphenmin=1 	file=loadhyph-mul-ethi.tex 	file_patterns=hyph-mul-ethi.pat.txt 	file_exceptions=
containersize 4460
containerchecksum a3fc85e7d1d84ecfc6bbdf16e06ae3f3475f975d59ece3f64d10cc1b24f05402018686eee1b7fccf7899633be67b1c0cbcbe7de78b0ecd93d45aa8d76872c690
srccontainersize 2620
srccontainerchecksum f7ba865dabe442354033b0220d7d00fa0901bf51f946ad65803329ea8af29f93ad649d9143071dd304f30a49651136cf106210490fa6aaf975c437f5ab4a5c07
runfiles size=5
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/loadhyph/loadhyph-mul-ethi.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/tex/hyph-mul-ethi.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/txt/hyph-mul-ethi.pat.txt
